## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **HFrEF four pillars** (2024 standard of care) = ARNI (sacubitril/valsartan) + β-blocker + MRA (spironolactone/finerenone) + SGLT2 inhibitor. quantum-VQE 의 selectivity 향상 path.
2. **HFpEF still challenging** — STEP-HFpEF (semaglutide) + EMPEROR-Preserved (empagliflozin) 첫 RCT positive. quantum-VQE 의 mechanism understanding 가능.
3. **AFib rate vs rhythm** = catheter ablation 이 standard 진정한 cure (rhythm). drug 는 rate control + DOAC anticoagulation. quantum-design 의 ion channel selectivity 향상.
4. **HCM mavacamten 2022** = first FDA myosin inhibitor; cross-link rare disease.
5. **PAH 5-class drug stratification** — endothelin / NO-cGMP / prostacyclin axes. quantum 의 mechanism-specific design.
6. **omecamtiv mecarbil 2022 FDA reject** = research evidence not enough; quantum-VQE 의 retry path.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, cardio 임상 의미 한정.

